Class AsperaTransactionImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.cloud.objectstorage.services.aspera.transfer.AsperaTransactionImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AsperaTransaction, AsperaTransfer

    public class AsperaTransactionImpl
extends Object
implements AsperaTransaction
    Class which provides access to the progress & status of a transfer. This object is returned to the user when any transfer process is started.
